== Projects ==
=== Object Tracking ===
[[File:Hackebein_object_tracking_wip.jpg|thumb|right|WIP screenshot of a tracker in VRChat]]
Track your real-world objects and use them in VRChat. This could include items like cups, chairs, poles, aerial hoops (lyra), guitars, decks, pets, cameras, or even your entire room. Various communities are forming around these possibilities <ref>https://vrchat.com/home/group/grp_b9665434-bcce-4260-bbdc-ae3b7c48edf0 - TRACKD.6559</ref>.

This project began in mid-2022 with the goal of synchronizing the rotation of my pole inside VRChat with its real-world speed. Initially focused on a single-axis rotation, the project has since evolved to support full six degrees of freedom (6DoF). Some Demos can be found on my Social Media Channels like this [https://x.com/Hackebein/status/1817729114142343460 Demo]

