=== Citizen of VRChat ===
It’s similar to an idle game but not confined to a single world. You earn points and unlocks based on your online activity and joinability. There are also bonus unlocks on special occasions like Christmas, New Year, Halloween, Valentine's Day, ... or when joining special events.

