=== Music Truck ===
[[File:Hackebein music truck wip.png|thumb|right|WIP screenshot of the truck model]]
An immersive in-game feature that allows you to create playlists collaboratively with friends and strangers, playing music within your instance as a separate user. This setup lets you control the music volume independently from user voices. The Music Truck also features a touchscreen interface for easy track searching and playlist management. Additionally, it offers the ability to paint a road on the ground and includes a system for attaching other trailers.

Currently on hold due to the low audio quality of the mic output in VRChat.

